import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['delay'] = pd.to_numeric(data['delay'], errors='coerce')
    data = data[pd.notna(data['delay'])]
    fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(10, 6))
    sns.histplot(data=data, x='delay', kde=True, color='blue', ax=ax)
    ax.axvline(data['delay'].median(), color='red', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=2, label=f'Median: {data["delay"].median():.2f}')
    ax.axvline(data['delay'].mean(), color='green', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=2, label=f'Mean: {data["delay"].mean():.2f}')
    ax.set_xlabel('Delay Time (minutes)')
    ax.set_ylabel('Frequency')
    ax.set_title('What is the distribution of delay time?')
    ax.legend()
    plt.show()
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['distance'] = pd.to_numeric(data['distance'], errors='coerce')
    data = data[pd.notna(data['distance'])]
    fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(8, 6))
    sns.barplot(x='distance', y='count', data=data, ax=ax, color='blue')
    ax.axvline(x=data['distance'].mean(), color='red', linestyle='--', label=f"Mean distance: {data['distance'].mean():.2f}")
    ax.set_xlabel('Distance')
    ax.set_ylabel('Count')
    ax.set_title('What is the average distance traveled by flights?')
    ax.legend()
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data = data.groupby(['origin', 'destination']).sum().reset_index()
    data = data.pivot('origin', 'destination', 'count')
    sns.heatmap(data, annot=True, fmt='d', cmap='YlGnBu')
    plt.xticks(rotation=45, ha='right')
    plt.yticks(rotation=0)
    plt.xlabel('Destination')
    plt.ylabel('Origin')
    plt.title('Which origin and destination pairs have the highest number of flights?')
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['date'], format='%Y-%m-%d', errors='coerce')
    data = data[pd.notna(data['date'])]
    fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(10, 6))
    sns.lineplot(x='date', y='count', data=data, ax=ax, color='blue')
    ax.set_title('What is the trend in flight count over time?')
    ax.set_xlabel('Date')
    ax.set_ylabel('Count')
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    return plt

chart = plot(data)

    plt.figure(figsize=(12, 8))

    plt.xlabel('Origin')
    plt.ylabel('Distance')
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
